> John
> =

> Would you agree that the square-metre loop is needed for the crystal
> set because a ferrite rod antenna does not capture enough power?
> =

> I think that is the case, simply because the ferrite rod is so much
> smaller, and produces less signal power, although it produces about a
> hundred times more power than the same small coil with the ferrite
> removed.
> =

> Alan G3NOQ
